kgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Btw星龜可愛熊貓好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熊貓根本就無生存意志，仲廢過樹獺<br />\n根本就抵死<br />\n<br />\n但有好多瀕危肉食動物都好得意，BB時期就更加<br />\n例如：老虎、獅子、象</blockquote><br />\n熊貓又懶又廢個樣成個on9仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee19cdc0e811ee5a2e682b1b7e9865504498021a","tid":110134,"uid":23701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:02:09.000Z","msg":"我有睇過本書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實個標題應該fake死唔小人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為佢個重點唔單只係人&mdash;養動物同人&mdash;食動物。<br />\n而係更大個課題咁討論，人&mdash;動物關係學既反思。<br />\n佢反思左好多，例如用動物黎做實驗啦，食動物啦，養動物啦，保護動物啦，鬥雞啦。<br />\n我有一個章節好深刻係，佢討論鬥雞同食雞。結論係相比起黎食雞既我地比鬥雞既人更加殘忍。<br />\n有興趣可以去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都好厚下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GB35fD7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGB35fD7.jpg&h=461eb2fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26e566abb7c0bddcdf7d36f86117dd3a8f6c5df","tid":110134,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:06:13.000Z","msg":"根本就証明左人係睇樣既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438a43f792d2db09279ca46339319c1e7553b26d","tid":110134,"uid":23701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:12:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本就証明左人係睇樣既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n書入面仲有個實驗係法國係街隨機問女女拎電話。<br />\n拖住隻狗既成功率比冇拖高30%<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分分鐘我地狗都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e287a2af3fad2c65ed7bc8eca452442915fb6b0","tid":110134,"uid":82576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:20:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>根本就証明左人係睇樣既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n書入面仲有個實驗係法國係街隨機問女女拎電話。<br />\n拖住隻狗既成功率比冇拖高30%<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分分鐘我地狗都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n怕狗點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10086fae83ec44479f1b964e1f8acaadbe980aba","tid":110134,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:23:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>根本就証明左人係睇樣既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n書入面仲有個實驗係法國係街隨機問女女拎電話。<br />\n拖住隻狗既成功率比冇拖高30%<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分分鐘我地狗都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n怕狗點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n怕係驚佢咬啫<br />\n<br />\n即係見到個靚女 但係渣住把刀又口up up話 你唔好埋黎呀<br />\n<br />\n你都會驚，但都覺得佢係靚女。係佢放低把刀之後就會去溝。"},{"pid":"9134ce3eadb48a3bc65d191639ead996aed0f64b","tid":110134,"uid":23701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:23:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>根本就証明左人係睇樣既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n書入面仲有個實驗係法國係街隨機問女女拎電話。<br />\n拖住隻狗既成功率比冇拖高30%<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分分鐘我地狗都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n怕狗點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女女怕定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c2a058c40c6b7c427af2a5503ba41758ad8cd0","tid":110134,"uid":82142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T03:31:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>本書大約講d咩 好有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n元朗公共圖書館好似有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n毒果都有介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/columnist/16455655/art/20120926/18024822\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fcolumnist%2F16455655%2Fart%2F20120926%2F18024822&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=6a336e4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fcolumnist%2F16455655%2Fart%2F20120926%2F18024822&h=46a43d8d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/columnist/16455655/art/20120926/18024822</a></blockquote><br />\n書中最大的分析，便是人類的雙重標準，甚至我們會因為動物的「可愛」而給予更高的地位。例如世界瀕危生物眾多，何以獨獨以熊貓作標記？答案：因為熊貓可愛囉。你不會用一隻瀕危的緬甸星龜作招徠，因為「唔夠可愛」，難以引起共鳴。<br />\n眾生平等，但可愛的動物，有更多的平等。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Btw星龜可愛熊貓好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熊貓根本就無生存意志，仲廢過樹獺<br />\n根本就抵死<br />\n<br />\n但有好多瀕危肉食動物都好得意，BB時期就更加<br />\n例如：老虎、獅子、象</blockquote><br />\n熊貓又懶又廢個樣成個on9仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n動物界廢青 廢老<br />\n連關愛座都唔識爭"},{"pid":"a8653df4900ff6980dfcd77aa40e363cd8aa9a24","tid":110134,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T11:46:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112e905e9b44ec6da40db6aa60d7e764dbe6c07d","tid":110134,"uid":14905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:30:53.000Z","msg":"留名睇"}]}